@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam classBorderColor #F57F17
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Completed
Completed --> Delivered : reject
Completed : entry / log classroom
Delivered --> Archived : cancel
Archived --> Active : cancel
Active --> Reviewed : reject
Reviewed --> [*]
@enduml